{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "6c092b03-67ec-453d-bdb5-304dc43fdcbf", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6c092b03-67ec-453d-bdb5-304dc43fdcbf@1.pkg/1772597669376/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597669913", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6c092b03-67ec-453d-bdb5-304dc43fdcbf@1.pkg/1772597669376/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597669913"}, "identifier": "6c092b03-67ec-453d-bdb5-304dc43fdcbf", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查生命的接续。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B：李某及其家属通过捐献器官，帮助5人重获新生，这是生命的接续，传递了生命的温暖和希望。故B说法正确；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A：李某及其家属通过捐献器官为他人带来了生命的延续，这是一种无私和大爱的表现，而不是追求个人的享乐。故A说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C：李某的家人在他离世后捐献器官，是出于对生命的尊重和珍视，为他人带来生的希望，而不是对生命的漠视。故C说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D：捐献器官并不是法定义务。故D说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）2025年8月8日，22岁的小伙李某因意外溺水死亡。他的父亲在极度悲痛中，做出了一个艰难却又温暖的决定：捐献儿子所有可用的器官，帮助5人重获新生。李某及其家属的行为（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）2025年8月8日，22岁的小伙李某因意外溺水死亡。他的父亲在极度悲痛中，做出了一个艰难却又温暖的决定：捐献儿子所有可用的器官，帮助5人重获新生。李某及其家属的行为（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6c092b03-67ec-453d-bdb5-304dc43fdcbf@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755245352653", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>启示我们要敬畏生命，及时享乐</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>传递了温暖，实现了生命的接续</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>是对人生命的漠视，不值得赞扬</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>诠释了生命的价值，履行了法定义务</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）2025年8月8日，22岁的小伙李某因意外溺水死亡。他的父亲在极度悲痛中，做出了一个艰难却又温暖的决定：捐献儿子所有可用的器官，帮助5人重获新生。李某及其家属的行为（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "par